title: Snapheal Pro - 1.2 [Intel/K]
description:
Snapheal is available in two versions, Standard and Professional. Both of the versions utilise same core features and offer the fastest and easiest way to remove unwanted objects. The difference is that Snapheal PRO uses more advanced spot healing technologies, works as plug-in and includes a number of other improvements.

NOTE: This is the PRO version, which means it's also works as a plugin within Photoshop, Lightroom, Aperture, etc. Run first in trial mode to install plugin, quit, then apply included crack/patch.
